FIELD.name: hjd
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Heliocentric Julian date (computed from mjd and the mean ra and dec of the input catalog)

FIELD.name: magerr
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty in mag measurement. Includes correction to conform to photometric repeatability RMS derived from "non-variable" population.

FIELD.name: catflags
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Catalog flags for source from PSF-fitting catalog

FIELD.name: filefracday
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Exposure file timestamp, with decimal representation YYYYMMDDdddddd: year, month, day, and fractional day

FIELD.name: limitmag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Approximate 5-sigma limiting magnitude corresponding to epoch-based PSF-fit catalog

FIELD.name: clrcounc
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Color coefficient uncertainty from linear fit

FIELD.name: airmass
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Airmass at approximately the center of the focal plane at time of exposure
